{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationDirection","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDirection","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"direction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The value "},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" means that the top edge of the map view corresponds to true"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"north. The value "},{"code":"90","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" means the top of the map is pointing due east. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value "},{"code":"180","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" means the top of the map points due south, and so on."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"code":"-setDirection:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The heading of the map, measured in degrees clockwise from true north.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"direction","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.